OL,3,CNo evidence former police chief misled
OL,4,CGuernsey's Royal Court
OL,6,FHowever, an investigation conducted by
OL,7,FWest Midlands Police concluded that no
OL,8,Fdocumentation or behaviour suggested
OL,9,FMr Hardy had misled the court.
OL,11,FThe report stated that no further
OL,12,Faction was needed and clarified that
OL,13,Fif the former Chief Officer was still
OL,14,Facting as a police officer, "there
OL,15,Fwould be no need for any disciplinary
OL,16,Faction to be taken."
