OL,3,CNo evidence former police chief misled
OL,4,CGuernsey's Royal Court
OL,6,FThe West Midlands Police report says:
OL,7,F"After reviewing all available
OL,8,Fdocumentation and corroborative
OL,9,Fevidence, the investigation did not
OL,10,Fidentify any behaviour or
OL,11,Fdocumentation that demonstrated an
OL,12,Fintention by Chief Officer Hardy to
OL,13,Fmislead the court."
OL,15,FIn a statement addressing the
OL,16,Ffindings, Ruari Hardy says: "The
OL,17,Foutcome of this investigation is not a
OL,18,Fsurprise to me, for I always acted
OL,19,Fwith honesty and integrity throughout
OL,20,Fmy 40-year career in policing.
