OL,3,CNo evidence former police chief misled
OL,4,CGuernsey's Royal Court
OL,6,F"My approach to the matter in question
OL,7,Fwas always based upon facts and
OL,8,Fdefendable decisions, with the safety
OL,9,Fof this island community at the
OL,10,Fforefront of my mind. This decision
OL,11,Fwas upheld by the Royal Court in
OL,12,FGuernsey, which was very clear that
OL,13,Fdenying access to a firearm license
OL,14,Fwas entirely appropriate based on the
OL,15,Fevidence available.
