OL,3,CNo evidence former police chief misled
OL,4,CGuernsey's Royal Court
OL,6,F"Whilst the barrage of inappropriate
OL,7,Fand unfounded allegations from this
OL,8,Fcomplainant has been distressing for
OL,9,Fme personally, it has been just as
OL,10,Fupsetting for serving officers and
OL,11,Ftheir families to witness.
OL,13,F"I am very pleased that this has now
OL,14,Fbeen concluded and that my integrity
OL,15,Fwhilst in office has been upheld."
OL,17,FMr Hardy retired last year, but this
OL,18,Fwas unrelated to the investigation.
