OL,6,F"As previously stated, it is also the
OL,7,FCommittee's view that Police
OL,8,FComplaints Legislation in Guernsey
OL,9,Frequires a fundamental and
OL,10,Fcomprehensive review, as a priority,
OL,11,Fto ensure it fully meets Policing
OL,12,FStandards and public requirements of
OL,13,F2025."
